    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Solid project or budget daily with strong old-school character. The powertrain fires up, pulls through the rev range, and the chassis still feels usable, making this a great candidate for someone who wants affordable transportation or a hands-on weekend refresh. Cosmetic wear and age-related flaws are present, but the car offers honest mechanical bones, straightforward serviceability, and plenty of value for an enthusiast who knows what to look for. If you want an inexpensive driver with potential, this one is worth a look.",
