      "description": "A diamond in the rough with unmistakable personality, this car has the kind of lived-in character that turns ordinary drives into a story. It\u2019s an ideal opportunity for someone looking for an affordable set of wheels, a hands-on project, or a practical backup ride with plenty of spirit left to give. The body and cabin show their journey, but that\u2019s part of its charm\u2014this is a car for someone who sees potential, value, and a little adventure in the everyday. If you want something inexpensive, honest, and full of possibility, this one is ready for its next chapter.",
      "price": 5995.0,
